page.title: 09WEEKEND'85--------E.WOODWARD
page.content: {FRIDAY 21ST JUNE-23RD JUNE I GOT HOME AND WATCHED T.V.I HAD SOME TOAST FOR TEA AND AFTER I SORTED SOME THINGS OUT FOR SCHOOL.I WENT TO MY GRANS AND WHEN I CAME HOME I WATCHED 'CAT'S EYES'ON T.V.AND WENT TO BED. {SATURDAY.}I WOKE UP AND WENT TO ROMAS TO HAVE MY HAIR CUT.I WENT ROUND ILKESTON AND THEN WENT HOME. AFTER DINNER I WENT SWIMMING. FOR TEA I HAD SAUSAGE,PEAS AND BEANS. I WENT TO MY ROOM TO READ FOR A WHILE AND THEN I WENT TO BED!{SUNDAY.}I WENT TO JUCOS AND THEN HELPED AT THE ALLOTMENT.I WENT TO DAWN'S PUB AND I EARNED Â£1.I WENT WITH HER TO NANNA'S AND WE WENT JOGGING ROUND THE 1 MILE GARDEN.WE HAD A PICNIC TEA AND THEN SUNBATHED.WE WENT JOGGING AND THEN PLAYED A GAME OF WALKING ROUND THIN EDGES.AT 8.00PM I WENT HOME AND I MADE A DRINK AND FINALLY WENT TO BED. {IT WAS GREAT!
